\b Movement - 
\b0 \
\
Style of movement & controls. Right now the dragon moves on a single pivot, which makes sense for a 2 legged character, or a creature with a short body. Dragons should drive by either their front or hind legs. \
\
The movement simulation can remain nonexistent like it is currently, or there incremental steps to simulating basics to really trying to capture character movement in depth.\
\
The dragons do need some level of physicality. There needs to be a difference between a small speedy dragon, and a big powerful dragon, and everything in-between. \
\
