\b Flight - 
\b0 \
\
Flight is in it's own separate category because it will behave very differently from ground controls. \
The transition to full flight would probably take intermediate steps, going from floaty jumps (like Yoshi's extended jump in Yoshi's island) to actually getting some forward momentum.\
\
The camera angle should change in full on flight mode and position behind the dragon since you will always be moving in a forward direction. \
\
In other games flight is a mode that toggles on and off, and the controls immediately change context. I imagine we will probably want more of a transition, where many of the controls you are already used to are still available while flying.\
\
I also think that elements like Wind speed and direction should play a big roll in flight. \
